869, "(fr)For this mission, we'll fly the $y GTB $y Boanerges, the Alliance's new attack bomber. The $y Boanerges maximizes shielding and payload, while offering enough manueverability to make it a viable tactical unit. The bomber won't handle as well as the Herc II, so stay on the move. Bombers make easy targets."

