1224, "(fr)Your primary target is the $h Iceni, $w Bosch's command ship. The $w 64th $w Raptors will lead the strike. The Vasudans will sortie the $f GVC $f Hyksos and a wing of $y Serapis fighters to assist. We will deploy additional forces as they become available."

